org.apache.geode.experimental.driver

Class RegionAttributes

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.geode.experimental.driver.RegionAttributes

  • @Experimental
public class RegionAttributes
extends java.lang.Object
    Encapsulates the attributes of a region in a GemFire server. This code is an experimental prototype and is presented "as is" with no warranty, suitability, or fitness of purpose implied.
